<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA624_03_IH_0002</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema624_03.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_03_ih_0002">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2_deep_green">
          <div class="mixed_fraction">
            <span>0.7:</span>
            <div class="fraction_box"><span>4</span><span>9</span></div>
          </div>
          <span lang="y">을 간단한 자연수의 비로 나타내려고 합니다. 두 가지 방법으로 나타내어 보세요.</span>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center align_start">
          <div class="img_area">
            <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_03_IH/0002_bg.png" alt="" />
            <div>
              <div class="l_left">
                <dl>
                  <dt>
                    <span class="label_method" lang="y">방법1</span>
                    <p lang="y">후항을 소수로 바꾸어 나타내기</p>
                  </dt>
                  <dd>
                    <div class="text_row">
                      <div class="mixed_fraction">
                        <span>0.7: </span>
                        <div class="fraction_box">
                          <span>3</span>
                          <span>5</span>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <img class="arrow" src="./../../common_practice/common/img/icon_arrow_right_navy.svg" alt="" />
                      <div class="flex align_center">
                        0.7:
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="0.6"></math-field>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="text_row">
                      <div class="blank"></div>
                      <img class="arrow" src="./../../common_practice/common/img/icon_arrow_right_navy.svg" alt="" />
                      <div class="flex align_center">
                        7:
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </dd>
                </dl>
              </div>
              <div class="l_right">
                <dl>
                  <dt>
                    <span class="label_method" lang="y">방법2</span>
                    <p lang="y">전항을 분수로 바꾸어 나타내기</p>
                  </dt>
                  <dd>
                    <div class="text_row">
                      <div class="mixed_fraction">
                        <span>0.7: </span>
                        <div class="fraction_box">
                          <span>3</span>
                          <span>5</span>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <img class="arrow" src="./../../common_practice/common/img/icon_arrow_right_navy.svg" alt="" />
                      <div class="flex align_center">
                        <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="(7)/(10)" class="w_80"></math-field>
                        </div>
                        :
                        <div class="fraction_box"><span>3</span><span>5</span></div>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="text_row">
                      <div class="blank"></div>
                      <img class="arrow" src="./../../common_practice/common/img/icon_arrow_right_navy.svg" alt="" />
                      <div class="flex align_center">
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field>
                        </div>
                        :6
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </dd>
                </dl>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
					<div class="inner_solve">
						<div class="flex">
							<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
							<div class="conts_solve">
                <p class="mixed_fraction">
                    <span class="fraction_box">
                      <span>3</span>
                      <span>5</span>
                    </span>
                    <span>=</span>
                    <span class="fraction_box">
                      <span>6</span>
                      <span>10</span>
                    </span>
                    <span>=0.6이므로 후항</span>
                    <span class="fraction_box">
                      <span>3</span>
                      <span>5</span>
                    </span>
                    <span> 을 0.6으로 바꾼 후 </span>
                </p>
                <p class="mt_15">0.7 : 0.6의 전항과 후항에 10을 곱하면 7 : 6이 됩니다.</p>
                <p class="mixed_fraction mt_15">
                  전항 0.7을
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>7</span>
                    <span>10</span>
                  </span>로 바꾼 후
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>7</span>
                    <span>10</span>
                  </span>
                  <span>:</span>
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>3</span>
                    <span>5</span>
                  </span>의 전항과 후항에 10을 곱하면 7 : 6이 됩니다.
                </p>           
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
